### The only rule is to include once `core.php` in all acessible page

##### You can put in in one header file and then include the header in other file

#### You can read readme in layout folder for more info about page functions

### The `.htaccess` file, is very important, dont loose it

### `404.php` is the error page, you can do what you want with it

### `sooon.php` is the page for cooming soon featuse, to enable it:
uncommnet these in '.htaccess' file:
``` php
# RewriteCond %{REQUEST_URI} !^/public/assets/ [NC]
# RewriteRule ^(.*)$ sooon.php [L]
```

### `assets` folder is where you will put your statics file there